================================
     Driver Forward
================================
Battery-powered system with a slide switch.

PWM (Pulse Width Modulation) Speed Control using analogWrite().


================================
SYSTEM BEHAVIOUR
================================
Motor rotates forward for 3 seconds
Stops for 2 seconds
Repeats continuously


